Border
1. In thai, border means ขอบ, ล้อมกรอบ

example
#file style.css
h1{
    border-style: solid;
    border-width: 3px;
    border-color: blueviolet;
    border-radius: 9px;
}
p{
    border-bottom: 3px solid red;
    border-top: 3px solid yellow;
    border-left: 3px solid green;
    border-right: 3px solid brown;
}

